# MarshalStream.RemoveWriteProcessor method

Unregisters a write processor.

```csharp
public bool RemoveWriteProcessor(IMarshalStreamProcessor processor)
```

| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| processor | The write processor to unregister. |

## Return Value

`true` if the write processor was successfully unregistered; `false` if the write processor was not registered.
